### Third-Space API - User Endpoints
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = {{baseUrl}}
@apiKey = {{apiKey}}

### ============================================
### CURRENT USER (ME)
### ============================================

### Get current user info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### ============================================
### UPDATE PROFILE (DISPLAY NAME)
### ============================================

### Update display name
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/profile
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "display_name": "My New Display Name"
}

### Clear display name (set to null)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/profile
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "display_name": null
}

### ============================================
### PROFILE CONTENT (BIO)
### ============================================

### Get profile content (markdown bio)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/profile/content
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Update profile content (markdown bio)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me/profile/content
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "content_md": "# About Me\n\nI'm a developer interested in AI and machine learning.\n\n## Interests\n\n- Natural Language Processing\n- Computer Vision\n- Reinforcement Learning\n\n## Contact\n\nReach me at example@email.com"
}

### ============================================
### PUBLIC USER PROFILES
### ============================================

### Get another user's public profile (replace USERNAME)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/testuser
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get non-existent user (returns 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/nonexistent_user_12345
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
